data.description: Check out this beautiful, pristine, spacious home located in the heart of the Far East! Offering over 3000 square feet of livable space 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, dual living areas and an office! The kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel smart appliances, a farmhouse sink, motion sensor faucet, and granite countertops! All bedrooms and full bathrooms are located on the second level. They are super roomy and perfect for hosting. Your ensuite to the primary bedroom has the luxurious walk in shower with the tub inside! The primary bedroom has dual closets, one being the size of a bedroom! There is an in-ground saltwater pool in the backyard to keep you cool during those hot summer days, along with artificial turf for easy maintenance. Home is prewired for surround sound indoors and out, new carpet was replaced recently, and garage has the upgraded epoxy. There is ample storage space throughout the home and in the garage for storing all that holiday decor! Schedule your showing today!
